JSX - Javascript syntax to create react elements.
Html or xml like syntax
JSX is not part of React. React & JSX both are different things. JSX makes developers life easy.
JSX is not html inside javascript.
JSX is not html.
JSX is a html like syntax.
JSX is not valid/Pure javascript. js engine does not understand this code.
Parcel => Babel is basically coverting/transpile JSX code to valid/pure javascript.
while giving attribute to JSX we need to follow camel casing ex - id, className, tabIndex etc.